{"id": "ChIJhwMu8UfGwoARU8hpiDf3VOE", "rating": 4.4, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_INEXPENSIVE", "userRatingCount": 416, "displayName": {"text": "Honeymee Japanese Village", "languageCode": "en"}, "editorialSummary": {"text": "Popular local chain spot known for milk ice cream with honey & other sweet treats.", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJhwMu8UfGwoARU8hpiDf3VOE/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pCWk5YazRZMWczYzJOUFNYb3dSVUpwVVZwSlFrRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "This is my favorite ice cream place to visit in Tokyo Town. The honey affogato is a must-order—the flavor is rich, not too sweet, and the texture is amazing. Everything comes together so well. Highly recommend stopping by if you’re nearby!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "This is my favorite ice cream place to visit in Tokyo Town. The honey affogato is a must-order—the flavor is rich, not too sweet, and the texture is amazing. Everything comes together so well. Highly recommend stopping by if you’re nearby!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Bruce jk Kim", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/117820444488965871044/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXxSSidTkelOShU-oZQYKTGNxpqlOAODAyLj471z_XGWakOMJU=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-17T05:00:43.537326284Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pCWk5YazRZMWczYzJOUFNYb3dSVUpwVVZwSlFrRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pCWk5YazRZMWczYzJOUFNYb3dSVUpwVVZwSlFrRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c647f12e0387:0xe154f7378869c853"}, {"name": "places/ChIJhwMu8UfGwoARU8hpiDf3VOE/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xOblYwRklRM2RJZW5oQk1sVnJXRGwwYzFOTmEwRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "The ice cream shop has some fun flavors and unusual tastes. It is not too sweet alone. I loved both items I tried. There was surprizingly ample seating and nice air conditioning. Staff was friendly and there is a photobooth inside.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "The ice cream shop has some fun flavors and unusual tastes. It is not too sweet alone. I loved both items I tried. There was surprizingly ample seating and nice air conditioning. Staff was friendly and there is a photobooth inside.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Carrie Smith", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102530781490188095292/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVjE5L90VfNIRVpJehEG6FgFJkZfQOnw0AhBf1XoimbU-ufFBd6Hg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-03-18T05:24:19.812987456Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xOblYwRklRM2RJZW5oQk1sVnJXRGwwYzFOTmEwRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xOblYwRklRM2RJZW5oQk1sVnJXRGwwYzFOTmEwRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c647f12e0387:0xe154f7378869c853"}, {"name": "places/ChIJhwMu8UfGwoARU8hpiDf3VOE/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pWWlRGaGFWRlZCYW1sQlJrbFFkR1kzUlZFeWVsRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "First time I've had this place and it did not disappoint! My friend recommended it so we all went together! The honey comb was very yummy with the ice cream I liked it a lot! Definitely need to come again.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "First time I've had this place and it did not disappoint! My friend recommended it so we all went together! The honey comb was very yummy with the ice cream I liked it a lot! Definitely need to come again.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Kensley Gray", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/113556912816228128855/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV3V-vk86OQMf0cVR-xcOre9hZu0bVBjQlK0AkkwFiXmpoZYWse=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-03T23:25:20.244963520Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pWWlRGaGFWRlZCYW1sQlJrbFFkR1kzUlZFeWVsRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pWWlRGaGFWRlZCYW1sQlJrbFFkR1kzUlZFeWVsRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c647f12e0387:0xe154f7378869c853"}, {"name": "places/ChIJhwMu8UfGwoARU8hpiDf3VOE/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21oSk9UVldiRXBEUXpWT2VXOUthbHBKYld4VFYwRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "6 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "We got two flavors of the ice cream. The matcha one is not too sweet or too bitter, we like them. The original honey one is little bit more sweet because of the honeycomb chip\nI think the store should upgrade their decorations, or more tables and chairs, it is too simple right now", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "We got two flavors of the ice cream. The matcha one is not too sweet or too bitter, we like them. The original honey one is little bit more sweet because of the honeycomb chip\nI think the store should upgrade their decorations, or more tables and chairs, it is too simple right now", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Minny D", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/114683979234483916800/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUSOX6eG8fjgGWBjGDIGptP3Cx6gCG-_Vf4iqdyHmSW4Qvk72w2=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-02T19:00:19.522004911Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21oSk9UVldiRXBEUXpWT2VXOUthbHBKYld4VFYwRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21oSk9UVldiRX